== Sant Basilacho gorabo ==
Sant Basilacho zolm eke girest familint zal'lo. 330 hea vorsa Pontus ganvant to zolmol'lo. Tachea bapaychem nanv Basil ani maichem nanv Emmilea axil'lem. Tacho ghorabo povitrtayek lagun nam'nek pavla. Tacho xapay [[Kristanvponn|Kristi dhormacho]] ek bolli zalo. Tache xamayn taka ani tachea char bavnnank, devache bhirantin voir kaddl'le.

== xikxonn ==
Basilak 350-351 hea vorsamni mullave xikxonn Cappadociachea Caesarea Mazaca (aiz Turkey)hea ghavant mell'lle. Thuy to Gregory hea nanvache mon'xeak bhetlo zo tacho jivit bor ek boro ixtt zalo. Uprant to ani tacho ixtt Gregory Constantinopoleak aple fuddle xikop gheunk gele. 

349 hea vorsa Athens nogrant to gelo ani thuy aplea ixtta sangata 6 vorsam ravlo, 356 vorsa to fuddlem xikop gheunk Egiptak, Syriak ani Mesodomiank pavlo ani xekim aplea ghanv gora Caesareant pavlo. Caesareant to advogad koso ani bhaxe vjnani koso vavurlo ani aple jivit tannem moujen sarlem.

Eka disa Sebaste nograntlea Govl'li bapak tachi bhett zali. To tachea jivita voir uloilo ani tednam St. Basilan aple jivit novsorle, tannem soglem soddun dilem soglli girestkay, tache xikop, somazant taka axil'li podvi, adim. Tache eke chittint tannem oxem boroilo'lem asa ki tannem soglo tacho vell ani tornatte jivit moujen vogdailem, tannem Devak chodd vell diunk nam, ovchituch to nidentlo uttlo oxem taka dislem ani xubhvortomanacho mog taka laglo ani devache podve vinnem kainch na hachi taka zann zali. Ani tannem aplem jivit Devak Bhettovpache taraylem. Apli sogli girestkay goribank vantli ani to aplem jivit eksurponnan Deva sangata sarunk laglo.


